### Note for `failed_wagers`

The `index` field of `failed_wagers` is the index of wager in request's wager list

```json
{
    "data": {
        "success": [],
        "failed_wagers": [
            {
                "request": {
                    "odds": 100,
                    "stake": 1000,
                    "line_id": "c8151bb0106b4225132e1eed71214e8c",
                    "external_id": "wager-fbfd34c6-779a-11ed-a1eb-2242ac000000"
                },
                "error": "wager_external_id_existed",
                "message": "event is not available for betting",
                "index": 0
            },
            {
                "request": {
                    "odds": 100,
                    "stake": 1000,
                    "line_id": "af92eecef365f00657df5da3f2d83d5c",
                    "external_id": "wager-fbfd34c6-779a-11ed-a1eb-2242ac000001"
                },
                "error": "wager_external_id_existed",
                "message": "event is not available for betting",
                "index": 1
            }
        ]
    }
}
```
